"All output geometries will be converted to multi geometries, even those with"
" just a single part. This algorithm does not dissolve overlapping geometries"
" - they will be collected together without modifying the shape of each "
"geometry part."
msgstr ""
"Alla utdatageometrier konverteras till multigeometrier, även de som bara har"
" en enda del. Den här algoritmen löser inte upp överlappande geometrier - de"
" samlas ihop utan att formen på varje geometridel ändras."

