"The output (convex hull) vector layer. Other than the input attributes, the "
"output layer also contains the following fields: ``area`` and ``perimeter`` "
"of the generated polygon."
msgstr ""
"Vektorlagret för utdata (konvex skrov). Förutom inmatningsattributen "
"innehåller utdatalagret också följande fält: ``area`` och ``perimeter`` för "
"den genererade polygonen."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1515
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:convexhull``"
msgstr "**Algoritm-ID**: ``native:convexhull``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1525
msgid "Create wedge buffers"
msgstr "Skapa kilbuffertar"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:1526
msgid "Creates wedge shaped buffers from input points."
msgstr "Skapar kilformade buffertar från inmatningspunkter."

