msgstr ""
"Ange utdatans linjevektorlager. :ref:`En av <output_parameter_widget>`:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3400
msgid "The output line vector layer split at the antimeridian."
msgstr "Utgångslinjens vektorlager delas vid antimeridianen."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3405
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:antimeridiansplit``"
msgstr "**Algoritm-ID**: ``native:antimeridiansplit``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3415
msgid "Geometry by expression"
msgstr "Geometri genom uttryck"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3416
msgid ""
"Updates existing geometries (or creates new geometries) for input features "
"by use of a QGIS expression."
msgstr ""
"Uppdaterar befintliga geometrier (eller skapar nya geometrier) för "
"indatafunktioner med hjälp av ett QGIS-uttryck."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3419
msgid ""
"This allows complex geometry modifications which can utilize all the "
"flexibility of the QGIS expression engine to manipulate and create "
"geometries for output features."
msgstr ""
"Detta möjliggör komplexa geometrimodifieringar som kan utnyttja all "
"flexibilitet i QGIS uttrycksmotor för att manipulera och skapa geometrier "
"för utdatafunktioner."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3423
msgid ""
"For help with QGIS expression functions, see the inbuilt help available in "
"the :ref:`expression builder <vector_expressions>`."
msgstr ""
"För hjälp med QGIS uttrycksfunktioner, se den inbyggda hjälp som finns i "
":ref:`expression builder <vector_expressions>`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3442
msgid "**Output geometry type**"
msgstr "**Typ av geometri för utdata**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3443
msgid "``OUTPUT_GEOMETRY``"
msgstr "``OUTPUT_GEOMETRY``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3447
msgid ""
"The output geometry strongly depends on the expression: for instance, if you"
" create a buffer the geometry type has to be polygon. One of:"
msgstr ""
"Geometrin för utdata är starkt beroende av uttrycket: om du t.ex. skapar en "
"buffert måste geometritypen vara polygon. En av följande:"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3452
msgid "0 --- Polygon"
msgstr "0 --- Polygon"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3453
msgid "1 --- Line"
msgstr "1 --- Linje"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:3454
msgid "2 --- Point"
msgstr "2 --- Punkt"

