"Rotates feature geometries by the specified angle clockwise. The rotation "
"occurs around each feature's centroid, or optionally around a unique preset "
"point."
msgstr ""
"Roterar objektgeometrier med den angivna vinkeln medurs. Rotationen sker "
"runt varje objekts centroid, eller valfritt runt en unik förinställd punkt."

