#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5857
msgid ""
"Specify the output vector layer (with segmentized geometries). :ref:`One of "
"<output_parameter_widget>`:"
msgstr ""
"Ange det utgående vektorlagret (med segmentiserade geometrier). :ref:`Ett av"
