msgstr "Det utgående vektorlagret med segmentiserade geometrier"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5806
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:segmentizebymaxangle``"
msgstr "**Algoritm-ID**: ``native:segmentizebymaxangle``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5816
msgid "Segmentize by maximum distance"
msgstr "Segmentiera efter maximalt avstånd"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5820
msgid ""
"The segmentization is performed by specifying the maximum allowed offset "
"distance between the original curve and the segmentized representation. Non-"
"curved geometries will be retained without change."
msgstr ""
"Segmentiseringen utförs genom att ange det maximalt tillåtna offsetavståndet"
" mellan originalkurvan och den segmentiserade representationen. Icke-krökta "
"geometrier behålls utan förändring."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5825
msgid ""
":ref:`qgissegmentizebymaxangle`, :ref:`qgissimplifygeometries`, "
":ref:`qgissmoothgeometry`"
msgstr ""
":ref:`qgissegmentizebymaxangle`, :ref:`qgissimplifygeometries`, "
":ref:`qgissmoothgeometry`"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5844
msgid "**Maximum offset distance**"
msgstr "**Maximalt offsetavstånd**"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5849
msgid ""
"Maximum allowed offset distance between the original curve and the "
"segmentized representation, in the layer units."
msgstr ""
"Maximalt tillåtet offsetavstånd mellan originalkurvan och den segmentiserade"
" representationen, i lagerenheter."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5884
msgid "**Algorithm ID**: ``native:segmentizebymaxdistance``"
msgstr "**Algoritm-ID**: ``native:segmentizebymaxdistance``"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5894
msgid "Set M value"
msgstr "Ställ in M-värde"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5895
msgid "Sets the M value for geometries in a layer."
msgstr "Ställer in M-värdet för geometrier i ett lager."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5897
msgid ""
"If M values already exist in the layer, they will be overwritten with the "
"new value. If no M values exist, the geometry will be upgraded to include M "
"values and the specified value used as the initial M value for all "
"geometries."
msgstr ""
"Om det redan finns M-värden i lagret skrivs de över med det nya värdet. Om "
"inga M-värden finns kommer geometrin att uppgraderas så att den innehåller "
"M-värden och det angivna värdet kommer att användas som det ursprungliga "
"M-värdet för alla geometrier."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5903
#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5990
msgid ""
"|checkbox| Allows :ref:`features in-place modification "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` of point, line, and polygon features with M "
"enabled"
msgstr ""
"|checkbox| Tillåter :ref:`features in-place modification "
"<processing_inplace_edit>` av punkt-, linje- och polygonfunktioner med M "
"aktiverat"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:5907
msgid ""
"Use the |identify|:sup:`Identify Features` button to check the added M "
"value: the results are available in the :guilabel:`Identify Results` dialog."
msgstr ""
"Använd knappen |identify|:sup:`Identifiera funktioner` för att kontrollera "
"det extra M-värdet: resultaten finns tillgängliga i dialogrutan "
":guilabel:`Identifiera resultat`."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/vectorgeometry.rst:7554
msgid "identify"
msgstr "identify"

